{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"Plan-review PASS (0 blocking, 8 advisory) already run this session but NOT yet claimed/implemented. Key advisories to honor when implementing: (1) add 'permissions: security-events: write' to the CodeQL workflow; (2) also run pip-audit in gerrit-verify.yaml if that is the gate CI, not only test.yml; (3) decide pip-audit failure policy (which severities fail; handle OSV DB network flake / --ignore-vuln for accepted); (4) pick pip-audit (not leave 'or OSV' ambiguous); (5) CodeQL push-to-main trigger is post-merge — acceptable for a Gerrit-gated mirror, document that. Attestation may be stale by resume (code drift) — re-run review-plan if claim is blocked."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783220311093589001,"uuid":"5f8e51d4-641c-4ec4-b527-fe5d969c8b28"}